No. 09-856. Angela Montgomery, Petitioner v. Wyeth, fka American Home Products Corporation, et al. 559 U.S. 1031, 130 S. Ct. 1896,

176 L. Ed. 2d 403,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 2415. March 22, 2010.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied. The

Chief Justice took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 580 F.3d 455.
